---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import { SITE } from '../data/site';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Brandtrove Privacy Policy—how we collect, use, and protect your personal information." path="/privacy-policy">
  <PageHero title="Privacy Policy" lead="How Brandtrove collects, uses, and protects your personal information." />

  <section class="section legal"><div class="container prose">
    <p class="legal-updated">Last updated: {SITE.legalUpdated}</p>
    <p>At Brandtrove, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains our practices when you visit our website or inquire about our strategic partnership services.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect information you voluntarily provide—such as name, email, company, phone, and partnership details—through contact forms, email, or direct communication.</p>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Facilitate strategic talent partnerships and project execution</li>
      <li>Communicate updates and respond to inquiries</li>
      <li>Analyze site performance and improve our services</li>
      <li>Meet legal and regulatory obligations</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>We implement technical and organizational measures to protect personal information. No internet transmission is 100% secure, but we strive to use commercially acceptable safeguards.</p>

    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>Brandtrove does not sell personal data. We share information only with service providers under contract, or when required by law.</p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>We may use cookies for essential functionality and performance analytics. See our <a href="/cookie-policy">Cookie Policy</a> for details.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You may request access, correction, or deletion of your data by contacting <a href={`mailto:${SITE.privacyEmail}`}>{SITE.privacyEmail}</a>.</p>

    <h2>International Transfers</h2>
    <p>As we facilitate global partnerships, data may be processed in countries other than your residence, with appropriate safeguards where required.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions: <a href={`mailto:${SITE.privacyEmail}`}>{SITE.privacyEmail}</a> or <a href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`}>{SITE.email}</a>.</p>
  </div></section>
</Layout>
